{"tid":35712,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人N個兒時老母用嚟嚇你嘅故事","createTime":"2016-12-12T09:08:27.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T12:14:33.000Z","uid":6854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ef9d7a06fbb31f344306bf5907048b542500642","tid":35712,"uid":6854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:08:27.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 從前有兩姊妹，姐姐訓上格床，妹妹訓下格，夜晚姐姐聽到下格床&quot;格⋯格⋯格&quot;聲，<br />\n就望落下格床見到媽媽坐係妹妹旁邊唔知食緊咩，就問：「媽咪，你食緊咩？」<br />\n媽媽：「冇呀，食薯片。」<br />\n第二朝姐姐落床，發現妹妹冇曬啲手指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 唔吹頭訓覺，個頭頂會生菇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前就係同家姐訓上下格床<br />\n完全唔明點解老母要咁嚇我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea608f6949c5c90bccd5bcd5aeba79ad6230ca9","tid":35712,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你大個要養哂成頭家"},{"pid":"0f0ede8dcc2a2996512b22ce24ad28abeba99c0b","tid":35712,"uid":26076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:10:52.000Z","msg":"食得多火龍果會變小火龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5989976e586a55d52084d8fa6bb467b399131c5a","tid":35712,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:11:22.000Z","msg":"唔讀書大過做黑衣（乞丐）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0bc57534ac620ecd474dbf0011f9b744c33c2a","tid":35712,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:11:40.000Z","msg":"唔乖就報警拉我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817982077cdb8ee35f8e907941021f676dd3c8e4","tid":35712,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:12:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔讀書大過做黑衣（乞丐）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你好似有懶音問題"},{"pid":"d8044c5f98e219b477568f48481deff26e73a808","tid":35712,"uid":7021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:12:55.000Z","msg":"我係執翻黎養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f660377208a3c63f0dc9cac21c50cd56a0f66e8","tid":35712,"uid":27510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:13:36.000Z","msg":"唔食埋淨翻一粒粒痴左係碗入面d飯會變痘皮佬/將來男朋友係痘皮佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446d8f98787924afb46622616c4c0e8e1310c468","tid":35712,"uid":34730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:15:23.000Z","msg":"你係石頭爆出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6f07e04aafa250eabfbc4a5df7d2f623a31bf5","tid":35712,"uid":6854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:15:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食得多火龍果會變小火龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n究竟你老母想你食多啲火龍果定唔食火龍果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd330532b7cb2cd174d15e5d3aace60b337a86f","tid":35712,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:20:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係石頭爆出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大聖<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f061e64529859de45af4e6310490f51911675e91","tid":35712,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:25:39.000Z","msg":"有一日，你死左"},{"pid":"2a75531f3e2d8dc17f3c63522d61704871643931","tid":35712,"uid":43978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:27:05.000Z","msg":"訓教啲手手腳腳唔可以伸出床如果㕶了係會比人斬左"},{"pid":"0ac0e59cd5e2445dec93b17936d9d8ec4c99da58","tid":35712,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:28:02.000Z","msg":"話當年佢喺大海度執我返嚟<br />\n我心諗，喺條街執又得，喺垃圾場執又得，點解係大海"},{"pid":"69921ac59af99586b4fb0be8f0fe850e377db280","tid":35712,"uid":6854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:31:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話當年佢喺大海度執我返嚟<br />\n我心諗，喺條街執又得，喺垃圾場執又得，點解係大海</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n究竟佢地咁講係為咗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79ccc4f45a4a0ea6b734aef816be1f6fd9e1cce6","tid":35712,"uid":7488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:32:35.000Z","msg":"唔好打鹽蛇 會走條尾入耳仔<br />\n唔聽話會比人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7df134fa435656442aa65661582f47123c37ed","tid":35712,"uid":5923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:36:49.000Z","msg":"牙齒唔x 會一直生 之後會隊串個嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7be373d48b2e40e0f6210d4319a23e37df12415","tid":35712,"uid":5923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:37:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>牙齒唔x 會一直生 之後會隊串個嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n穿"},{"pid":"42ebdaf68fe1569260fdca30f6780c73a4717a5e","tid":35712,"uid":2730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:41:17.000Z","msg":"橋底會有丫烏婆捉小朋友，一定要拖實媽咪！"},{"pid":"cf6c205e88d7b8d41b1cab52284c74cb0ed3eef2","tid":35712,"uid":6854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:51:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>橋底會有丫烏婆捉小朋友，一定要拖實媽咪！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我老母都成日咁講 <br />\n搞到我細個勁驚啲呀婆"},{"pid":"87b02a1e5e852aba00639e7e9a98f819afdb68df","tid":35712,"uid":2730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:57:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>橋底會有丫烏婆捉小朋友，一定要拖實媽咪！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我老母都成日咁講 <br />\n搞到我細個勁驚啲呀婆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有去大陸過關一定要拖實，因為有拐子佬捉小朋友去賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c03caf85236cddbdf4063292acb8e77baeb239","tid":35712,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:08:51.000Z","msg":"食格夜蛋個春袋會大過自己個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bfd6ac249a44c3fa29e5d2857e653cbca234280","tid":35712,"uid":6854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:09:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>橋底會有丫烏婆捉小朋友，一定要拖實媽咪！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我老母都成日咁講 <br />\n搞到我細個勁驚啲呀婆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有去大陸過關一定要拖實，因為有拐子佬捉小朋友去賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依啲話叫做嚇你驚你有危險都算<br />\n我老母會仲會臨訓前同我講&quot;床下底有隻冇頭鬼&quot;<br />\n根本就係以嚇我為樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e3c8ae412c5231445d38ac468ae9cc798d09c7","tid":35712,"uid":2730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:21:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我老母都成日咁講 <br />\n搞到我細個勁驚啲呀婆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有去大陸過關一定要拖實，因為有拐子佬捉小朋友去賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依啲話叫做嚇你驚你有危險都算<br />\n我老母會仲會臨訓前同我講&quot;床下底有隻冇頭鬼&quot;<br />\n根本就係以嚇我為樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n訓唔著啦實會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b7fdfa4333bab8cc64c8f671f0bbb28e996ca68","tid":35712,"uid":59219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:35:19.000Z","msg":"老豆就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細個呃我話屋企門口有盞路燈上面坐住隻女鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個陣時好驚<br />\n雖然佢十年前同我講返其實係假 不過到而家次次經過都要快步行<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}